headline: A. O. Smith Stock Outlook: Is Wall Street Bullish or Bearish?
summary: Although A. O. Smith has considerably underperformed the broader market over the past 52 weeks, Wall Street analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook about the stock’s prospects.
